data.value:
Expense App is a personal and group financial management application developed by the VNG Dev Team, students of the Faculty of Information Technology, University of Science – VNU HCM. The app aims to help users record detailed daily transactions, analyze their spending habits, and most importantly, manage shared expenses transparently within groups such as friends, families, or roommates.
With a clean and user-friendly interface, Expense App offers an efficient and intuitive experience. It integrates essential features such as account management, personal income/expense tracking, group expense sharing, financial reports, and user feedback – all within a single system.
This project was developed as part of the Object-Oriented Programming (OOP) course, under the guidance of Mr. Vo Nhat Tan and Mr. Truong Tan Khoa. We believe that the app is not only a valuable academic exercise but also a practical tool for effective everyday financial management.
